by Thomas E. Bartlett, Adam M. Sykulski, Sofia C. Olhede, Jonathan M. Lilly and Jeffrey J. Early (2015) 

email: thomas.bartlett.10@ucl.ac.uk with queries

All code is in Matlab, and all downloads are zip files.

SPVNT.zip
  - code to perform a power variance test on any complex-valued signal

Figs156.zip
  - code to exactly replicate Figures 1, 5 and 6

Figs234.zip
  - code to exactly replicate Figures 2, 3 and 4
